SELECT 
                        do_masuk.no_do,
                        do_masuk.jumlah_ayam_jantan + do_masuk.jumlah_ayam_betina AS jumlah_ayam,
                        do_masuk.jantan_mati + do_masuk.betina_mati AS jumlah_ayam_mati,
                        do_masuk.berat_ayam_jantan + do_masuk.berat_ayam_betina AS berat_ayam_pembelian,
                        do_masuk.harga_ayam,
                        (do_masuk.berat_ayam_jantan + do_masuk.berat_ayam_betina) * do_masuk.harga_ayam AS total_modal,
                        SUM(penjualan.berat_ayam) AS berat_ayam_penjualan,
                        SUM(penjualan.berat_ayam) - (do_masuk.berat_ayam_jantan + do_masuk.berat_ayam_betina) AS susut_surplus,
                        SUM(penjualan.net_penjualan_ayam) AS net_penjualan_ayam,
                        SUM(penjualan.net_penjualan_ayam) - ((do_masuk.berat_ayam_jantan + do_masuk.berat_ayam_betina) * harga_ayam) AS laba_rugi 
                    FROM 
                        do_masuk
                    INNER JOIN
                        kartu_stock ON kartu_stock.no_do = do_masuk.no_do AND kartu_stock.penjualan_id IS NOT NULL
                    INNER JOIN
                        penjualan ON penjualan.penjualan_id = kartu_stock.penjualan_id
                    WHERE 
                        do_masuk.tipe_do = 'A' AND MONTH(do_masuk.tanggal) = '05' AND YEAR(do_masuk.tanggal) = '2022'
                    GROUP BY 
                        do_masuk.no_do

WITH profitnloss AS (
                        SELECT
                            MONTH(penjualan.tanggal) AS bulan,
                            SUM(penjualan.net_penjualan_ayam) - (do_masuk.harga_ayam * SUM(penjualan.berat_ayam)) - SUM(penjualan.pengeluaran) AS laba_rugi
                        FROM
                            penjualan
                        INNER JOIN
                            kartu_stock ON kartu_stock.penjualan_id = penjualan.penjualan_id
                        INNER JOIN
                            do_masuk ON do_masuk.no_do = kartu_stock.no_do
                        WHERE
                            penjualan.MIN = 0 AND YEAR(penjualan.tanggal) = 2022
                        GROUP BY
                            MONTH(penjualan.tanggal),
                            do_masuk.harga_ayam
                        )
                    SELECT 
                        bulan, 
                        SUM(laba_rugi) AS laba_rugi 
                    FROM 
                        profitnloss 
                    GROUP BY 
                        bulan

                    DAY(penjualan.tanggal) AS tanggal,

                    AVG(penjualan.berat_rata_ayam) AS berat_rata_ayam,
                    AVG(penjualan.harga_satuan_ayam) AS harga_rata_rata,
                    SUM(penjualan.berat_ayam) AS total_berat_ayam,
                    SUM(penjualan.net_penjualan_ayam) AS total_penjualan_ayam
                FROM
                    penjualan
